Invocation Name: course conductor
Developer Terms of Use
des: Course Conductor enables companies to drastically reduce the cost of selecting training vendors, make more informed buying decisions, and reduce the risk of wasting valuable resources on ineffective, low-quality training. We publish independent industry reports called Trusted Training Radar Reports that are based on customer reviews about a wide range of professional training. Based on the content of the Trusted Training Radar Reports we award training vendors with a status of Leader, High Performer or Contender.
